{"tid":2225821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"便衣笑九南丫海難街","createTime":"2020-10-01T15:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:13:27.000Z","uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d23cb8818c00f531e429390746d9a529ab8c5df","tid":2225821,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w14leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=6c9fbe25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&h=e1933378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/</a>"},{"pid":"16e73b477549c659892c9a487c52576c4509ac0a","tid":2225821,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"【警察：溪錢係垃圾￼、你唔好消費海難，唔好做戲】<br />\n南丫八周年悼念￼￼￼￼，家屬及蓮姐於中環碼頭擺設祭壇悼念￼。警察突然介入，是八年來第一次。警察在祭壇前指責溪錢是垃圾￼，並指罵蓮姐消費海難死難者，在做戲。￼蓮姐是一名自發悼念的市民，￼￼八年來風雨不改在國 __ 日悼念39名死難者，而且完全自費。<br />\n蓮姐傷痛欲絕，痛哭啜泣，情緒激動一度暈倒。最後警方發出一張599i 告票￼￼￼￼￼。￼<br />\n警方對海難的調查尚未完成，所以死因裁判庭未能開始審訊， 39名死難者八年後的今日仍然未正式被政府發出死亡證。￼"}]}